sets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲戇鳩仔，完全喺到消磨所有人嘅耐性，助長負面情緒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母我真係唔撚知有件咁嘅事啊嘛，碌碌下post無撚啦啦畀你屌，唔撚知唔撚得架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人知冇人提咁咪你提話人知囉我屌你老母，你知又唔撚講其他人唔知又可以點撚樣講啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接收資訊嗰個一定要畀發放資訊嗰個屌架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪你細個你老竇教你寫字嗰陣一路教一路屌你老母先教到你呢啲撚樣出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母臭閪谷鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33436d2ddf6b3b36849432ff55ad67897118601f","tid":2248602,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"樓主未來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b765b00b0e6039343945948f23ffd432215769","tid":2248602,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"樓主勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17b85bc35e04d12a63d71cd4b62a5f0a432bbcb","tid":2248602,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:18:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d8f6f2d020b2669c25fd69b749bc468b781e23b","tid":2248602,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:19:54.000Z","msg":"完場洗唔洗沖涼"},{"pid":"39d86614f6d1c6bc731b02e215cb183cff349025","tid":2248602,"uid":213844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"淨係輸緊先換出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9320df4c6233cbc1c957659ee6cce385c9c001c5","tid":2248602,"uid":8450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:26:46.000Z","msg":"人來人往？"},{"pid":"fe315ad0d64249f078f2351c7aa2f54e92d332a3","tid":224860